{
  "stem": "14060.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You put it in before the domestic or the non-Jewish person lit the fire for the purposes of heating the room.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was perfectly acceptable, and that way we had hot water and hot milk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, that is just giving you, by the way, how lifestyle went.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the afternoon, we used to go out in the-- in the nearby forest, which this was a holiday resort as well, besides having had five universities.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a very pretty town, and it can be still inspected today, except there are no Jews left there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, my only connection with it is my two grandparents of my father's parents, who died before I was born.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Their graves are there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And strangely enough, they remained intact.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they have beautiful, large, black granite stones, which I somewhat had, with my cousin together, put in more solid [INAUDIBLE], but they were always there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They died in the late '20s.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A few years ago, I read that there were some vandalism in that cemetery, even so, they had a permanent caretaker there all the years, from '45 during the Communist times, even today.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I knew the guy, because I went there a few times after 30 years when I went back to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was some vandalism.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You wouldn't believe it, what the story was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The story was that these were Germans who came in from Austria to vandalize a cemetery in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, such a story put on its head.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Those German or Austrian hooligans find enough Jewish cemeteries where they can do damage locally.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They don't have to come into another country to do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But this is the method and the-- today's mentality, even, it had nothing to do with us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We are not at fault.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
